query:
SELECT name, slug, 
  IF(overview IS NOT NULL AND overview != '', 'YES', 'NO') as has_overview,
  IF(topThingsToDo IS NOT NULL AND topThingsToDo != '', 'YES', 'NO') as has_activities,
  IF(attractions IS NOT NULL AND attractions != '', 'YES', 'NO') as has_attractions,
  IF(foodCafes IS NOT NULL AND foodCafes != '', 'YES', 'NO') as has_food,
  IF(threeDayItinerary IS NOT NULL AND threeDayItinerary != '', 'YES', 'NO') as has_itinerary
FROM island_guides 
WHERE name IN ('Himmafushi', 'Omadhoo', 'Feridhoo', 'Dhangethi', 'Mathiveri', 'Gulhi', 'Goidhoo', 'Fulhadhoo', 'Fehendhoo', 'Hanimadhoo', 'Fuvahmulah')
ORDER BY name
